  "title": "Admin Assistants(Diploma, Cashew MRT)",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Scope</p>\n<p>1. Provide administrative support to NSREC   admin and operations.<br>\n    2. Working knowledge or   proficient in MS Word and Excel.<br>\n    3. Process oriented and able to   work well on data details.<br>\n    4. Good spoken and written   English and other languages if any.<br>\n    5. Experience with customer   services if any.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>1) At least Diploma holder<br>\n2) 1 to 2 years of admin working experiences <br>\n3) Good interpersonal and communicate skills (oral and written)<br>\n4) Must uphold strong code of work ethnics and confidentiality of information<br>\n5) Detailed and meticulous<br>\n6) Able to work under pressure to meet deadlines<br>\n7) Good working knowledge of Microsoft Office, especially in using MS Excel</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please submit resumes to john@oaktree.com.sg with the following details in MS Word format:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Position applying for</p>\n<p>- Current remuneration</p>\n<p>- Expected remuneration</p>\n<p>- Notice period</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>John Goh Meng Chye</p>\n<p>EA License No : 06C4642</p>\n<p>EA Reg No : R1102621</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
